text: College Holiday is a 1936 American musical comedy movie directed by Frank Tuttle and starring Jack Benny, George Burns, Gracie Allen, Mary Boland, Marsha Hunt, Leif Erickson, Martha Raye. It was distributed by Paramount Pictures. ==Other websites== * * Category:1936 comedy movies Category:1930s American musical movies Category:American musical comedy movies Category:Movies directed by Frank Tuttle Category:Paramount Pictures movies
